<title key="Almond and roe pastry">Zu <dish commodity="Q0" en="soft food">geweichten</dish> <religion>Inder vasten</religion></title> 
<instruction>NIm <ingredient en="almond" commodity="Q184357">mandel</ingredient></instruction> vnd 
<instruction>hakch den chlain</instruction> vnd 
<instruction>verb den halben mit <ingredient en="saffron" commodity="Q25434">saffran</ingredient></instruction> 
<instruction>das leg besunder In ain <tool en="bowl" commodity="Q153988">schuessel</tool></instruction> 
<instruction>nym <ingredient en="grape" commodity="Q10978">weinper</ingredient> wol erlesen</instruction> vnd 
<instruction>well die daz sie sinibel werden</instruction> vnd 
<instruction>leg die besunder in die <tool en="bowl" commodity="Q153988">schussel</tool></instruction> 
<instruction>zu disen nym aller <ingredient en="roe" commodity="Q219426">visch rogen</ingredient></instruction> <kitchenTip>den der <ingredient commodity="Q107246431" en="barbel's roe" ana="exclusion">pearbem rogen</ingredient> nicht</kitchenTip> vnd 
<instruction>die in einen <tool en="mortar" commodity="Q45778">morser</tool> mit einem wenigen <ingredient en="wheat flour" commodity="Q2249305">weissn melblen</ingredient> daz ez werd als ain <ingredient commodity="Q107261752" en="funnel cake dough">straubem taig</ingredient></instruction> vnd 
<instruction>ferb das</instruction> vnd 
<instruction>geuz auf die <dish commodity="Q0" en="flat cake">fladen</dish></instruction> vnd 
<instruction>pach es in einem <tool en="baking oven" commodity="Q36539">oeffen</tool></instruction></div></body></text></TEI>